data.description: This fantastic home has served her young military family well during their stay here in San Antonio...They absolutely loved the neighborhood and surrounding amenities, restaurants, shopping, and entertainment, that the stone oak area has to offer. A stones throw from the highly ranked elementary school, this 1.5 story home has 3bd / 2.5ba downstairs with a flex room in the front to be used however you like ! Oh, and almost 200 sqft upstairs to utilize however you see fit ! Priced to sell, and one of the very few 1 story homes available in the area. **Previous Listing has photos of house empty**
